values: I barely even log onto Furc anymore. I remember when Furc was just starting out and my brother and I got on. We were greeted by some chick named Sylvea Moon and her boyfriend Mental Man. My colors were an uncoordinated mess and I wanted wings more than anything. The left side of the screen was just brown, and there weren't any buttons to make it easier, you had to learn every command. We had no clue how to make a halfway decent dream, had no idea what to do, and had no idea that we would make so many friends. Sylvea Moon became like, my best friend. xD In all.. I sort of miss the awe that Furc gave me 4 years ago. Now it seems like some sort of distant memory, but in all honesty I sometimes wish that it was the way it was way back when. I guess I'm just living in the past.

I'm having an awesome summer.
Some update.

I'm changing. I promise. I will realize something. No matter how many new friends I make IRL. I will never forget the times I spent with my friends online. I will never abandon them and treat them differently again. Because they're no less. 

I really REALLY feel like shit for what I did to Rydia. REALLY. It has got to be the most horrible thing I've done all year. Rydia, I again, am so SO sorry. I fucked up. I acted like one of the people I despise most. And it was disgusting. I can only hope you'll understand my dilemma. I am SO sorry.

Morgaine told me to update this.

SO.

I'm studying for Biology. I've been pretty well lately. I don't know about all y'all but I wish I heard from you more often. =\
I'm making my journal friends only, afraid of people who shouldn't be reading stuff, reading stuff. >.>; If you want to read it, Get a livejournal, ask me, and you might get that privilege. =)

Geez.. How could something so great always end up so terrible. Take for instance, my relationship. Maybe if I wasn't a fucking moron I would've realized that my relationship didn't exist. But somehow, I forgot that I'd broken up. I've gotta be the world's biggest idiot. But yeah, I bet I've lost him for good this time. And that's ok I suppose, because he deserves better than me.. I was always suspicious and jealous and I never had a reason to be.. But.. I guess that's just the way things always gotta work out for Lance. Today, I was supposed to hang out with a friend. But because of miscommunication, I didn't get to have that opportunity, effectively ruining tonight AND tomorrow for me. Wow, what a great life I lead. Right now I would be having a great time, but no, I'm stuck here where my life always falls apart. What an excellent life it is that I lead. And please, stop IMing me and telling me that I should stop bitching in my journal because it really bothers me. A journal is for personal thoughts. If I had good thoughts I'd write them. I don't. So shut the fuck up. Thanks.

I'm back.. A lot of people hadn't even realized I'm gone.. But the ones who did.. They E-mailed me and called me until I came back.. And I'm glad I did.. And I'm sorry for running off without a word like that..  but I wanted to leave everything behind.. But.. I realized.. What I've formed.. I can never leave behind.. Thanks to Vap and Kutiah.. Who really did their best to make me feel better.. =\

Thinking about all that stuff, Draco read my journal and dragged me to the pond.. All of my friends showed up, as if on cue.. And we had a great time, laughing and screaming and joking again... It was amazing, people I haven't seen in MONTHS started showing up. It was so great. It made me so much happier. All thanks to Draco. Thanks Draco. =)

Today, I actually talked to a lot of people.. And it's kind of really unhappy actually. Just talking to everybody and seeing how much they've changed since I first met them... It was 3 years ago that I first discovered the internet... It was 3 years that I met all of my old friends... Here or gone... Most gone... And it's kind of sad. We all used to be such children.. Now they've all grown up and become so much more mature, and it seems like I'm the only one who got left behind. Still a child. Missing out on life, because I'm so naive and blind to so much stuff.

While babysitting Satan's children, I sat online and talked to people. And talked. And talked. And talked. So many people tell me that they look up to me, that they think I'm really something else.. That they actually *worship* me. I don't understand this at all. Of all the people you should never look up to, you should never look up to me. All you guys are all so great and so amazing at like everything, why would you look up to me who's just.. not?

Anyway, that wasn't even the saddest part of my day. I remember how I was even more naive last year... Guys... All of my old friends.. I want you to think.. Think back to last year.. When we used to all sit at the pond.. Everyday, the pond would be full to capacity, so full, that many seats on the ground with and without pillows were taken because there wasn't enough seats for us. There was never any asking, "Have you seen" or "Where has ? been" because we were always so well informed.. The closest of friends.. Every single night we would sit and talk and joke and laugh and just have a great time.. It was amazing. I considered everybody here to be like brothers, closer than anybody I knew IRL.. Closer than everything that I ever loved.. I mean, I was at the point of naivity where I thought we would stay this way forever. Meet IRL. Have fun. But no, none of that ever happened.. We fell apart, and look at us now. Spend ONE entire day at the pond and maybe 3 people who used to be there all day will show up for 4 minutes. It's just depressing... Everybody's went their separate ways.. Everybody's different, new friends, new interests. Am I the only one who misses it? Am I the only one who even thinks of it anymore. I mean, I mention some things that we used to do people and they go, "What?" "Huh?" "I don't remember." You've all forgotten.. Forgotten what great friends we used to be.. And it's a shame. =\

Sanguis continues to work hard for my journal's betterment. Thankies. =)

I think I've lost Tristan again.. He's disappeared yet again... Or... He just doesn't care and is avoiding me or whatever... Do I honestly deserve this? I mean... I thought he actually loved me... What's the matter with me?
